data.title: Vocal harmony singing group
data.text:
Jacob Narverud : Bones

So if you're asking me, sayin', Oh, how do you know? I don't just feel it in my heart, I feel it in my bones. Recorded by Galantis featuring OneRepublic, this dance hit is superbly set for mixed voices as well as for men's choirs. The high energy, rock groove and lyric-filled arrangement will be a standout for any pop performance and has a CD or digital download track as well as instrumentation available.

Arranger: Jacob Narverud Performed By: OneRepublic

Voicing: SATB | Sheet Music | $2.50 |

(Minimum order 4 copies) | 00293628 | Digital Version Available| Showtrax CD Available

Other Voicings: SAB, TTB, TTB, SAB

Mark Brymer : Counting Stars

The band OneRepublic performs music that reflects many musical influences, from rock to pop to indie and more. This hit from 2013 has a driving rhythm and unforgettable chorus that will electrify your stage! Duration: ca. 3:00

Arranger: Mark Brymer | Composer: Ryan Tedder Performed By: OneRepublic

Voicing: 2-Part | Sheet Music | $2.75 | With Piano |

(Minimum order 4 copies) | 00124156 | Digital Version Available| Showtrax CD Available

Other Voicings: 3-Part, SATB, 3-Part, SATB

Deke Sharon : Good Life

Here is the 2011 pop hit by OneRepublic as arranged by a cappella guru Deke Sharon for Tim Seelig and the San Francisco Gay Men's Chorus in a vibrant and joyful setting! The lyrics may not be suitable for every choir, so be sure to preview it first!

Arranger: Deke Sharon Performed By: OneRepublic

Voicing: TTBB | Sheet Music | $2.25 | A Cappella |

(Minimum order 4 copies) | 00116329 | Digital Version Available

Jacob Narverud : I Lived

With an uplifting and universal message, this favored tune of carpe diem was recorded by OneRepublic on their album Native and has become an anthem of hope and empowerment. The arrangement stays true to the original song and allows choirs to rock out while singing meaningful lyrics.

Arranger: Jacob Narverud | Composer: Ryan Tedder Performed By: OneRepublic

Voicing: SATB | Sheet Music | $2.75 | With Piano |

(Minimum order 4 copies) | 35030369 | Digital Version Available| Showtrax CD Available

Other Voicings: SAB, SSA, SAB, SSA

Deke Sharon : I Lived

A Cappella groups will enjoy performing this song by OneRepublic, with an uplifting and universal message and all the energy and excitement of the original!

Mark Brymer : Love Runs Out

Fans of OneRepublic's Counting Stars will love this song from their third album with its pounding drum track and driving piano rhythm. More rock than pop, this song will energize your performers with its unique sound.

Arranger: Mark Brymer | Composer: Ryan Tedder, Brent Kutzle, Drew Brown, Zach Filkins, Eddie Fisher Performed By: OneRepublic

Voicing: SATB | Sheet Music | $2.50 | With Piano |

(Minimum order 4 copies) | 00137968 | Digital Version Available| Showtrax CD Available

Other Voicings: SAB, 2-Part, 2-Part, SAB

Jacob Narverud : Run

Ryan Tedder, the lead vocalist for the pop rock band OneRepublic, has made a living out of being a musician, TV personality, songwriter, and record producer for some of the hottest names in popular music. This energetic, propulsive song directly mirrors Ryan's thirst for the hustle and the never-ending search for optimism and drive in unprecedented times.

Arranger: Jacob Narverud Performed By: OneRepublic

Voicing: SATB | Sheet Music | $2.50 |

(Minimum order 4 copies) | 00390874 | Digital Version Available
